author: Home Repair Tutor
description: I cut the plank tile around my closet flange using the Outlaw blade and polished it with the small chamfer cone. I also use large chamfer cones for cuts like this, and they’re a great help. Many thanks to Kipp from Rock Steady Tools for sending these supplies 🙏🏼🔥#tilefloor #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
